; background:#0C7ABF;\">PLEASE CLICK HERE TO LOG ONTO THE SETA GRANT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM</a>\n                                                </td>\n                                             </tr>\n                                          </table>\n\n                                       </td>\n                                    </tr>\n\n\n <tr>\n\n                                    <td>\n\n                                        <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">VERY IMPORTANT INSTRUCTIONS TO THE LEARNERS\n\n\n                                       </p>\n\n\n                                          <ul>\n                                             <li style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:28px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px 0px;  \"><b>1. OLUMS SETA PORTAL APP</b></li>\n\n                                      <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">You are able to perform all your functions online via the OLUMS SETA PORTAL App.   If you do not own a smart phone, you can carry out all your tasks by logging onto the SETA PORTAL WEBSITE <a style=\"color:#489FDF; text-decoration:underline;\" href=\"(--HOME_URL--)\"> www.setaportal.co.za</a>.  Everything that you can do on the App, can be done via the Website. \n\n                                       </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                                             <li style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:28px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px 0px; ;\"><b>2. ENSURE THAT THE SUPERVISORS INFORMATION IS CORRECT</b></li>\n\n\n                                 \n                                     \n                                      <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">The Learner must ensure that the Supervisors contact information is correct on the SETA PORTAL.  If the Learner is assigned to a new Supervisor, they must immediately CONTACT US to update the new Supervisor\'s information\n\n                                       </p>\n\n                             \n\n                                 \n\n                                             <li style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:28px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px 0px; \"><b>3. ONLINE DAILY ATTENDANCE REGISTER</b></li>\n\n                                              \n                                      <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">Log your Daily Attendance on the online Attendance Register via the App or via the website.\n\n                                       </p>\n                                         <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">Please note that your physical location GPS of your workstation must be registered by your Supervisor.  Please Chat with your Supervisor to Register the GPS Location of your Work Station via the OLUMS SETA PORTAL APP.  The GPS registration of workstation can only be done via the OLUMS SETA PORTAL APP.   The Supervisors must then ASSIGN the Registered Workstation to you. The Supervisors can re-sign your Workstation at any time if you work at different Locations.\n                                       </p>\n                                         <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">Your Supervisor may not be aware of the OLUMS SETA PORTAL APP feature of Registering the GPS Location of each Workstation and assigning it to the Learners.\n                                       </p>\n \n                                   <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">PLEASE NOTE THAT FAILURE TO LOG YOUR DAILY ATTENDANCE REGISTER WILL RESULT IN YOUR MONTHLY STIPEND CLAIM BEING REJECTED\n                                       </p>\n\n                                    \n\n\n\n                                             <li style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:28px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px 0px;\"><b>4. PROGRESS REPORTS </b></li>\n                                               <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">All Learners MUST complete the Progress Reports via the SETA PORTAL APP or via the website www.setaportal.co.za.  Supervisors can view your Progress Reports and provide comments and guidance.  All the Progress Reports will be compiled into a PDF Portfolio of Evidence which will then be available to the SETA MANAGERS AND LEARNERS\n                                       </p>\n\n\n                                             <li style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:28px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px 0px;\"><b>5. SUBMISSION OF MONTHLY STIPEND CLAIMS  </b></li>\n                                               <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">All Learners are required to Submit their Monthly Claims Online at a date provided by the SETA GRANT ADMINISTRATORS.  \n                                       </p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">After the Claim had been Submitted by the Learner, the Supervisor is Alerted via the Seta Portal App and via their Email to Approve the Stipend Claim.  After the Stipend Claim had been approved by the Supervisor, the Stipend Claims will thereafter be processed by the Grant Administrators \n                                       </p>\n\n                                    \n                                            \n                                        <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">You need to be aware that if you did not Log your daily attendance on the online Attendance Register, your Stipend Claim may be rejected by the Grant Admin \n                                      \n                                       </p>\n\n                                       <li style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:28px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px 0px; \"><b>6. CHANGE OF BANKING DETAILS  </b></li>\n                                               <p style=\"margin-top:0px; font-weight:500; line-height:24px; color:#333; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:0.2px; text-transform:none; padding:10px 4px;\">Please note that if your Bank Account details had changed, you MUST immediately update such changes on the SETA PORTAL and Upload evidence from the Bank such as a Bank Statement, to confirm your banking account details.  Failure to comply will result in your Stipend Claim being paid into the wrong Bank Account.  \n                                       </p>\n                                          </ul>\n                                       </td>\n                       